byline.original: By CHRIS BUCKLEY and ADAM WU

lead_paragraph: An official with the land and resources bureau in a city in southwest China wounded the mayor and the Communist Party secretary at a meeting, news reports said.
snippet: An official with the land and resources bureau in a city in southwest China wounded the mayor and the Communist Party secretary at a meeting, news reports said....

headline.main: Chinese City Official Shoots 2 Others and Kills Himself, State Media Says
headline.print_headline: Gunfire, Suicide and a Meeting in China
